  <brief_title>0.05 Versus 0.1 mg Spinal Morphine for Reducing Morphine Requirement After Vaginal Hysterectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Comparison of 0.05 vs. 0.1 Milligram Spinal Morphine for Reducing Morphine Requirement After Vaginal Hysterectomy With/Without Anterior and Posterior Vaginoplasty</official_title>
  <sponsors>
