  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to compare the efficacy of 0.05 mg and 0.1 mg spinal morphine in reducing
      postoperative morphine requirement in patients undergoing vaginal hysterectomy with/without
      anterior and posterior vaginoplasty.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
